    format("Yo! Champ in the making!\p Let me give you some advice!\p The LEADER, MISTY, is a pro who uses WATER-type POKMON.\p You can drain all their water with GRASS-type POKMON.\p Or, you might use ELECTRIC-type POKMON and zap them!")
}

